taudio-engines
==============

This repository contains packaging, manifests, download/cache helpers, and
vendored open-source engine libraries (when present under libs/).

Umbrella license for original packaging code in this repository: MIT
(see LICENSE).

Third-party components
----------------------

Upstream licenses for vendored libraries must be recorded here and copied
under licenses/<component>/ when those libraries are added.

| Component | Upstream | SPDX | Notes |
|-----------|----------|------|-------|
| (none yet) | | | MVP libs will be added in follow-up PRs |

Model weights are NOT distributed in this git repository. Each model entry in
manifest.yaml declares its download URL(s), checksum, and license. Runtime
code downloads weights into a local cache directory.
